#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:1
msgid "E0069"
msgstr "E0069"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `declaration_implemented`"
msgstr "警告名称：`declaration_implemented`"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:5
msgid "Declaration is already implemented."
msgstr "声明已实现。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:7
msgid ""
"This warning is emitted when a `declare` item already has a matching "
"implementation in the same package. At that point the declaration is "
"redundant: the implementation itself is enough for the compiler to know "
"the API."
msgstr ""
"当 `declare` 条目在同一个包中已经有对应实现时，会发出此警告。此时该声明是多余"
"的：实现本身已经足以让编译器了解这个 API。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:11
msgid ""
"This warning is useful when declarations were added during a refactor and"
" should be removed after the implementation has landed."
msgstr ""
"如果在重构过程中添加了声明，并希望在实现落地后删除这些声明，此警告会很有用。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:14
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:16
msgid ""
"declare fn f() -> Unit\n"
"\n"
"fn f() -> Unit {\n"
"  println(\"only\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"declare fn f() -> Unit\n"
"\n"
"fn f() -> Unit {\n"
"  println(\"only\")\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:20
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:22
msgid "Remove the redundant declaration and keep the implementation:"
msgstr "移除多余的声明，保留实现："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0069.md:24
msgid ""
"fn f() -> Unit {\n"
"  println(\"only\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"fn f() -> Unit {\n"
"  println(\"only\")\n"
"}\n"
